These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
2 different pets are kept: cat, lizard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, banana
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, march
House: townhouse, gothic-revival
City: hamburg, new-york
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person eating banana is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Pet         | lizard  | cat       |
| Flower           | bellflower   | poppy    |
| Food   | banana     | pumpkin   |
| Birthday   | march      | may     |
| House         | gothic-revival | townhouse      |
| City     | new-york       | hamburg           |

