.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, davidoff
2 different games are played: billiard, snooker
House: colonial, gothic-revival
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, pop
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, lacrosse
1. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the game-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Cigar      | davidoff         | game       |
| Game          | billiard        | snooker |
| House           | gothic-revival | colonial    |
| Flower   | lily        | poppy  |
| Music-Genre   | pop        | electronic       |
| Pet           | rat            | cat        |
| Sport     | lacrosse            | rowing       |

