2. the person eating broccoli is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating broccoli is the person watching action movies##1
6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
